snippet.title: Moonfrost: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Moonfrost is a modern day life-sim farming RPG set in a beautiful next gen pixel-art world.

Embark on an epic journey filled with secrets, wonder and charming characters. It’s time to see what we have in store for you!

Join our community: https://discord.gg/moonfrost

Stay updated on all our news by following us on our other social platforms:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/MoonfrostGame
Medium: https://medium.com/@moonfrost
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MoonfrostGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/moonfrostgame

#Moonfrost #pixelgames #indiegames #farmgame #pixelart
